    <title>解決 localhost 返回 ::1 而非 127.0.0.1 的問題</title>
    <link>https://malagege.github.io/blog/posts/%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA-localhost-%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E-1-%E8%80%8C%E9%9D%9E-127.0.0.1-%E7%9A%84%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C/</link>
    <pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 22:49:47 &#43;0800</pubDate>
    <author>malagege</author>
    <guid>https://malagege.github.io/blog/posts/%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA-localhost-%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E-1-%E8%80%8C%E9%9D%9E-127.0.0.1-%E7%9A%84%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C/</guid>
    <description><![CDATA[<div class="featured-image">
                <img src="https://gist.github.com/assets/6058558/e7822d8c-db53-483a-8981-b123f4f164e3" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
            </div><p>有時候程式明明只想針對本機連線做白名單判斷，結果抓到的不是 127.0.0.1，而是 ::1。第一次看到會很像系統解析錯誤，但其實這通常只是 IPv6 和 IPv4 的差異。</p>]]></description>
</item>
<item>
    <title>Chrome 莫名其妙 localhost 會導到 HTTPS</title>
    <link>https://malagege.github.io/blog/posts/Chrome-%E8%8E%AB%E5%90%8D%E5%85%B6%E5%A6%99-localhost-%E6%9C%83%E5%B0%8E%E5%88%B0-HTTPS/</link>
    <pubDate>Sun, 22 Aug 2021 15:43:28 &#43;0000</pubDate>
    <author>malagege</author>
    <guid>https://malagege.github.io/blog/posts/Chrome-%E8%8E%AB%E5%90%8D%E5%85%B6%E5%A6%99-localhost-%E6%9C%83%E5%B0%8E%E5%88%B0-HTTPS/</guid>
    <description><![CDATA[<p>上次在本機用 mkcert 搭配 Vite 架過 HTTPS，當時一切正常。結果後來我把開發站切回 HTTP，Chrome 卻還是硬把 <code>localhost</code> 導去 HTTPS，一開始只能靠無痕視窗暫時繞過，後來才認真查清楚，根本原因大多跟 HSTS 有關。</p>]]></description>
</item>
